OL,3,CIsrael and Iran trade retaliatory
OL,4,Cstrikes for first time since April
OL,6,FIsrael and Iran have traded fire in
OL,7,Fretaliatory strikes for the first time
OL,8,Fsince April in a move that threatens
OL,9,Fto drag the region back into full-
OL,10,Fscale conflict.
OL,12,FCentral and western Iran were hit by
OL,13,FIsraeli strikes early on Monday
OL,14,Fmorning in response to missiles from
OL,15,FTehran, making it the most serious
OL,16,Fcrossfire since an April 8 ceasefire
OL,17,Fbegan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
