CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780945877
OL,3,CIsrael and Iran trade retaliatory
OL,4,Cstrikes for first time since April
OL,6,FThe sound of explosions could be heard
OL,7,Fin Isfahan, Karaj, Tabriz and Tehran,
OL,8,Fand the airspace was closed around
OL,9,FTehran's Imam Khomeini International
OL,10,FAirport, according to Iranian state
OL,11,Fmedia.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FIsraeli authorities then warned that
OL,19,Ftwo waves of Iranian missiles were
OL,20,Ftargeting the country, and urged the
OL,21,Fpublic to seek shelter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780945877
OL,3,CIsrael and Iran trade retaliatory
OL,4,Cstrikes for first time since April
OL,6,FExplosions could be heard in central
OL,7,FIsrael as the nation's air defences
OL,8,Fsought to intercept the incoming fire.
OL,10,FMissile alert sirens were also heard
OL,11,Fin Saudi Arabia on Monday morning, in
OL,12,Fan area home to an air base that hosts
OL,13,FUS forces, but the nation later said
OL,14,Fthe missile danger had passed without
OL,15,Felaborating further.
OL,17,FIran first fired missiles at Israel on
OL,18,FSunday in retaliation for airstrikes
OL,19,Fon the southern suburbs of Beirut,
OL,20,Fwhich killed two people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
