OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780945877
OL,3,CIsrael and Iran trade retaliatory
OL,4,Cstrikes for first time since April
OL,6,FIran had warned that an attack on
OL,7,FBeirut would renew full-scale war
OL,8,Facross the Middle East, despite
OL,9,Fongoing talks between Tehran and
OL,10,FWashington.
OL,12,FThe price of Brent Crude oil, the
OL,13,Fglobal benchmark, spiked on Monday
OL,14,Fmorning by more than 4% to $97.39
OL,15,F(#72.97) a barrel.
OL,17,FThe White House has not yet commented
OL,18,Fon the strikes and whether they were
OL,19,Fdone in coordination with the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
