OL,3,CIsrael and Iran trade retaliatory
OL,4,Cstrikes for first time since April
OL,6,FA senior US official on Sunday said
OL,7,Fpresident Donald Trump had called
OL,8,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,9,FNetanyahu to urge him not to retaliate
OL,10,Fimmediately for the Iranian missile
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FThe official, who spoke on condition
OL,14,Fof anonymity to describe the private
OL,15,Fphone call, said Trump believed he had
OL,16,Fconvinced Netanyahu to wait.
OL,18,FThe US president told Iran, "you've
OL,19,Fshot your missiles, that's enough"
OL,20,Fwhen asked about the nation's attack
OL,21,Fon Israel by Fox News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
